Canary Wharf May Buy Debt Backing Citigroup U.K. Tower, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-06-14T01:06:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-14/canary-wharf-may-buy-debt-backing-citigroup-u-k-tower-ft-says.html
Canary Wharf  Group Plc is in
exclusive discussions with  Royal Bank of Scotland Group Plc (RBS)  to
purchase more than 150 million pounds ($245 million) of debt
behind the Citigroup Inc. tower in London, which is being sold
by its private investor owners, Glenn Maud and Derek Quinlan,
for more than 1 billion pounds, the Financial Times reported,
without saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 